Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Vestar Capital Partners, Inc. operates as a private equity firm. The Company specializing in management buyouts, recapitalizations, and growth equity investments. Vestar Capital Partners serves customers in the States of New York, Colorado, and Massachusetts.




